"title": "8245: ethics, incentives towards",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8245: ethics, incentives towards",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's ethical demands are reinforced by a variety of sanctions and incentives.</p>\n<h2>Sanctions promoting ethical behaviour</h2>\n<h3>The authorities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:3-Rom13:4\">ROM 13:3–13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:18\">DEU 16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:11-Deut17:12\">DEU 17:11–17:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:1\">DEU 25:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3-Ps82:4\">PSA 82:3–82:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1-1Tim2:4\">1TI 2:1–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>God treats people as they treat others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:14-Matt6:15\">MAT 6:14–6:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:9-2Sam12:10\">2SA 12:9–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:7\">MAT 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:2\">MAT 7:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:35\">MAT 18:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:13\">JAS 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Unethical behaviour renders worship unacceptable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:4\">ISA 58:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:13-Isa1:15\">ISA 1:13–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:31\">EZK 33:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:5\">ZEC 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:9-Zech7:10\">ZEC 7:9–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42\">LUK 11:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:16\">TIT 1:16</a></p>\n<h3>The withdrawal of God's fellowship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:2\">ISA 59:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:11\">PSA 51:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:18\">PSA 66:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:6\">HOS 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:4\">MIC 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:30\">EPH 4:30</a></p>\n<h3>God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:8\">GAL 6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15\">DEU 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:23-Isa1:24\">ISA 1:23–1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9\">1CO 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:10\">2CO 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5-Col3:6\">COL 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:14\">HEB 12:14</a></p>\n<h2>Incentives to correct ethical behaviour</h2>\n<h3>A new life in Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8\">EPH 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:2\">ROM 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:13\">ROM 6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:15\">2CO 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:9-Col3:10\">COL 3:9–3:10</a></p>\n<h3>God's goodness and love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1-Eph5:2\">EPH 5:1–5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:2\">EXO 20:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:8-2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:8–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:14\">TIT 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>Pleasing God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:16\">HEB 13:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:9\">2CO 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20\">COL 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:3-1Thess2:4\">1TH 2:3–2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:1\">1TH 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:22\">1JN 3:22</a></p>\n<h3>True worship is made possible</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:3\">PRO 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">HOS 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:6-Isa58:7\">ISA 58:6–58:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:33\">MRK 12:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>\n<h3>God's fellowship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12-Deut10:13\">DEU 10:12–10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps15:1-Ps15:5\">PSA 15:1–15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:7\">REV 21:7</a></p>\n<h3>God's blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:20\">DEU 16:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:2\">DEU 28:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:3\">PSA 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:11\">PSA 84:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:1-Isa56:2\">ISA 56:1–56:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:9-Isa58:14\">ISA 58:9–58:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:18\">MAT 6:18</a></p>\n<h3>Future reward</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:13-Luke14:14\">LUK 14:13–14:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:42\">MAT 10:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:41\">MRK 9:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:36\">MAT 25:34–25:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:35\">LUK 6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:10\">ROM 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:24\">COL 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:12\">REV 22:12</a></p>",
